The '''anti-personnel laser cannon''' was a light laser cannon that was designed for killing infantry personnel. It was used on vehicles like the [[All Terrain Tactical Enforcer/Legends|AT-TE]], [[OG-9 homing spider droid/Legends|OG-9 homing spider droid]] and [[HAVw A6 Juggernaut/Legends|Clone Turbo Tank]].

